The paper is about a machine learning algorithm that is designed to be robust to outliers, which is a common problem in many areas of machine learning. The paper focuses on the application of the algorithm to two specific datasets, one related to drug design and the other related to spam classification. Based on this, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
